usage:	./corewar [-utlcv] [-dump[64|32] nbr_cycles] [-n number[1..4]] <name.cor> ...
	-u	: show this message
	-t	: listen to the tune
	-l	: system leaks
	-c	: enable colors
	-v	: enable visualization
	-dump nbr_cycles : after nbr_cycles dump the memory and quit the game (64 or 32 octets per line)
	-n number[1..4]	 : set number of player(champ) to `number`
	<name.cor> ...	 : up to the 4 champions in one battle
	//-d - different levels of detalisation